public.vw_services_with_levels.name: vw_services_with_levels
public.vw_services_with_levels.definition: SELECT s.id, s.name, s.service_date, s.status, s.created_by, s.created_at, s.locked_after_ingestion, s.service_type, s.devotion_type, s.gender_constraint, s.service_time, array_agg(l.code ORDER BY l.code) AS level_codes, array_agg(l.name ORDER BY l.code) AS level_names, count(sl.level_id) AS level_count FROM services s LEFT JOIN service_levels sl ON s.id = sl.service_id LEFT JOIN levels l ON sl.level_id = l.id GROUP BY s.id, s.name, s.service_date, s.service_time, s.service_type, s.devotion_type, s.gender_constraint, s.status, s.created_at

public.vw_service_level_details.name: vw_service_level_details
public.vw_service_level_details.definition: SELECT s.id AS service_id, s.name AS service_name, s.service_date, s.service_time, s.service_type, l.id AS level_id, l.code AS level_code, l.name AS level_name, sl.created_at AS assigned_at FROM services s JOIN service_levels sl ON s.id = sl.service_id JOIN levels l ON sl.level_id = l.id ORDER BY s.service_date DESC, s.service_time, l.code

public.vw_services_with_datetime.name: vw_services_with_datetime
public.vw_services_with_datetime.definition: SELECT id, name, service_date, status, created_by, created_at, locked_after_ingestion, service_type, devotion_type, gender_constraint, service_time, service_date + service_time AS service_datetime FROM services

public.vw_recent_admin_actions.name: vw_recent_admin_actions
public.vw_recent_admin_actions.definition: SELECT aa.id, aa.action, aa.created_at, aa.object_type, aa.object_label, concat(a.first_name, ' ', a.last_name) AS admin_name FROM admin_actions aa JOIN admins a ON aa.admin_id = a.id ORDER BY aa.created_at DESC LIMIT 50
